{{Infobox Berry |name = Watmel |image = [[File:Watmel.png]] |caption = A bounty of nature that is exceedingly sweet. The Berry is huge, with some discovered that exceed 20 inches. |growtime = 4h 36m 0s |harvest = 32 berries |replant = 10% |points = 1,000 |flavor = {{!}} 0 {{!}} 0 {{!}} 30 {{!}} 10 {{!}} 0 }} '''Watmel''' is a type of [[Berries|Berry]] that can be planted in [[Farm]]. It can be obtained by surrounding a [[Magost]] with at least 130, but no more than 160 points of sweet and no more than 80 points of all other flavours. The [[Magost]] will then have a chance to mutate into this berry.
